[Heroku](https://www.heroku.com/) is one of the most popular cloud [platform as a service](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Platform_as_a_service). It started with Ruby on Rails but it now supports many programming languages and frameworks. It allows you to easily deploy your application using Git. It helps you focus more on the functionality of the application rather than infrastructure. Heroku also offers a command line tool that makes it easier for you to manage your applications.
